00:40:05,550 --> 00:40:07,530
I need to know a bit about him in advance.

880
00:40:07,530 --> 00:40:08,530
Don't worry.

881
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:11,400
Minister Wen is charming and elegant,

882
00:40:11,420 --> 00:40:12,670
handsome and talented.

883
00:40:12,670 --> 00:40:13,510
He's cultured when needed

884
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,880
and strong when required.

885
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:16,740
