936
00:42:00,650 --> 00:42:02,460
close as internal organs.

937
00:42:04,070 --> 00:42:05,300
This watch isn't that valuable.

938
00:42:05,300 --> 00:42:07,160
I bought it at a secondhand stall.

939
00:42:07,710 --> 00:42:09,440
The parts were all rusted then.

940
00:42:09,590 --> 00:42:10,760
I fixed it myself.

941
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:12,780
I hope it's accurate.

942
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:14,240
Accurate. Very accurate.

943
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:17,130
And what was that phrase you used earlier,

944
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:18,900
close as internal organs?

945
00:42:19,760 --> 00:42:21,790
You meant 'close to the skin', right?

946
00:42:21,790 --> 00:42:23,710
Right, it's close to my skin.

947
00:42:24,040 --> 00:42:25,850
