00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:36,880
Huang,

951
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:39,850
I also ordered a plain noodle soup.

952
00:42:39,880 --> 00:42:41,100
Could you go check on it?

953
00:42:41,100 --> 00:42:42,110
I'll go see.

954
00:42:42,110 --> 00:42:43,360
Go hurry them up.

955
00:42:48,960 --> 00:42:49,710
How is it?

956
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,550
She's from south.

957
00:42:52,960 --> 00:42:55,030
Highly educated and artistic.

958
00:42:55,670 --> 00:42:56,600
What do you mean?

959
00:42:57,880 --> 00:42:59,010
Introduce her to me?

960
00:43:00,230 --> 00:43:01,230
Stop pretending.

961
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:02,230
Stop being so picky.

962
00:43:02,230 --> 00:43:03,480
She's good enough.

963
00:43:03,670 --> 00:43:04,800
Do you even know her?

964
00:43:07,280 --> 00:43:08,840
How did you even meet

965
00:43:10,840 --> 00:43:11,960
